Overview

Silapathar Town College is a well known College / Institute based in Dhemaji, Assam, India and established /founded in the 1993 is a modern educational institution. Silapathar Town College is a Private) College and offers education mainly in ARTS/SCIENCE/ENGINEERING/ LAW ETC. The main object of the institute is to provide quality education to enhance individual performance and elevate professional standards through innovative training programs in varied disciplines, research and extension activities.

Silapathar Town College has established itself as an institute of great repute in the area of ARTS/SCIENCE/ENGINEERING/ LAW ETC. Join us in building a successful partnership in carving a great future and embark on a fascinating journey with Silapathar Town College
